$magic targets weren't hit so have been rotating my stables to $gala and $osmo. Hoping gala convincingly breaks out of this downtrend, best case scenario for me is it approaches highs and magic continues to range lower this month. https://t.co/WY9pSWSHn8
There's a lot of luck involved in finding gems in this space but you get the most value from these opportunities by doing what you can to help them shine.

I honestly spent more time playing Town Star, working to be the best at it, writing about it, and assisting people in the discord interested in learning the game than I did making modules for my students and preparing for the online classes I was responsible for that schoolyear.

That I was getting that much $gala from referrals is a reflection of the time, effort, and hustle I put in contributing to Gala's early growth by being an active community member & creating content https://t.co/CdE8jOncRt

The other day the persistent rewards for referrals running their own Gala nodes were stopped. I now receive 37.5% less gala/day and this is healthier for the ecosystem as a whole. It was decided through a governance vote by node owners last Nov and I proudly voted in favor of it.
